game.name: Frozen Elsa Prep
game.description:
This time the cute and very gorgeous Frozen Elsa has planned to go for the prom tonight! She has made all the preparations except finalizing a perfect costume to wear on the party. Your dynamic fashion abilities have allowed you to earn good rapport in the society. Due to your immense popularity as a stylist, she has hired you as her personal designer. Join Frozen Elsa Prep and get ready to prove her decision right! Both sides of the screen will show you the lovely makeup and dressing options. 

It is up to you how to react fast to impress her friends through her impressive look in this brand new dressing game for girls! She is very concerned about her face look so try to apply all the tools including blush, mascara, eyeliner, eye shadow, eyebrow maker and lipstick to give her a matchless makeup. Once you realize that you are done with the make-up part, make sure to click the next button and browse through her extensive collection of outfits and accessories. She is waiting to be dressed up in an exclusively-designed outfit. 

Start with an awesome hairstyle and then combine it with a short dress or a full-length gown supported by a matching shrug! Give your girl a pair of suitable earnings and a beautiful necklace set in this cool html5 girls game! Pair her look with a pair of fabulous sandals and give magical power in her hands! Click the show button to see how your efforts have made a difference in making her look really gorgeous!
